title: Playoff teams that won't be back
itunes:title: Playoff teams that won't be back
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – discuss the latest NFL news including Andrew Luck’s new contract and the suspensions of Sheldon Richardson, Johnny Manziel and Ronaldo McClain. Then the Heroes discuss the best defensive lines in the NFL before wrapping the podcast predicting which 2015 playoff teams won’t make it back in 2016. Plus, what’s wrong with the Irishman?
